text:
You handled everything until the end.
Well done, Tenka.

Tenka? Even though you can go home now,
you seem a bit lonely.

...Come to think of it, I let you win last time, didn't I?
Why don't we stop by the arcade one last time?

Tenka wants to go...!
...Oh, but... is that okay...?
Yeah, we should have enough time for that...

I can't go home just losing all the time!
Let's go, Tenka!
